OL,3,CAm I entitled to a #1,000 payout for
OL,4,Cmy prepayment meter - and how do I
OL,5,Cclaim?
OL,7,FThousands of energy customers are set
OL,8,Fto receive payouts from #40 to #1,000,
OL,9,Fafter energy regulator Ofgem ordered
OL,10,Fsuppliers to compensate customers over
OL,11,Fthe forced fitting of prepayment
OL,12,Fmeters.
OL,14,FThis follows a lengthy investigation
OL,15,Fby Ofgem into the treatment of
OL,16,Fcustomers who had prepayment meters
OL,17,Ffitted in the middle of the cost of
OL,18,Fliving crisis as energy bills began to
OL,19,Fsoar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
