OL,3,CAm I entitled to a #1,000 payout for
OL,4,Cmy prepayment meter - and how do I
OL,5,Cclaim?
OL,7,FThis order will see energy providers
OL,8,Fdivvy out more than #70m in
OL,9,Fcompensation and financial aid to
OL,10,Fcustomers, but how do you know if
OL,11,Fyou're due a payout?
OL,13,FWhy is this payment being made?
OL,15,FThe payouts follow an investigation by
OL,16,Fthe regulator into the forced fitting
OL,17,Fof prepayment meters, something that
OL,18,Fincreased two years ago during the
OL,19,Fcost of living crisis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
