OL,3,CAm I entitled to a #1,000 payout for
OL,4,Cmy prepayment meter - and how do I
OL,5,Cclaim?
OL,7,FEnergy companies were found to be
OL,8,Fforcibly switching customers who were
OL,9,Fstruggling to pay their bills over to
OL,10,Fprepayment meters.
OL,12,FThis was a time when energy bills
OL,13,Fsharply increased as the global price
OL,14,Fof gas and oil was affected by
OL,15,FRussia's invasion of Ukraine.
OL,17,FFollowing the discovery of these
OL,18,Fforced switches, Ofgem suspended all
OL,19,Fforced installations and launched a
OL,20,Freview of the process which has now
OL,21,Fmade recommendations for compensation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
