OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FWho is eligible?
OL,14,FOfgem said suppliers have committed to
OL,15,Fpay both additional compensation where
OL,16,Fit is due, and in some cases write off
OL,17,Fsome energy debt of customers who had
OL,18,Fan involuntary prepayment meter
OL,19,Finstalled during the assessment period
OL,20,Fof January 1, 2022 to January 31, 2023.
