OL,7,FThe #74m compensation package is being
OL,8,Fsplit between eight suppliers.
OL,10,FBetween them, #55m in support has
OL,11,Falready been distributed, with #13m
OL,12,Fmore earmarked to write off customer
OL,13,Fdebt and the remaining #5.6m
OL,14,Fcompensation for the near 40,000
OL,15,Fcustomers affected.
OL,17,FThe eight companies ordered to make
OL,18,Fpayments are:
