OL,3,CAm I entitled to a #1,000 payout for
OL,4,Cmy prepayment meter - and how do I
OL,5,Cclaim?
OL,7,F"Involuntary installations have been a
OL,8,Flast - but necessary - resort for
OL,9,Fcases where repeated attempts to
OL,10,Faddress debt with the customer through
OL,11,Fother means have been unsuccessful.
OL,12,FIt's bad for customers to fall further
OL,13,Fand further into arrears, and bad debt
OL,14,Fultimately drives up the prices that
OL,15,Fare paid by all customers.
OL,17,F"Since the pause on installations,
OL,18,Fcustomer debt has risen to a record
OL,19,F#4b, and the industry remains keen to
OL,20,Fwork with Ofgem on the proposed relief
OL,21,Fscheme to tackle this problem."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
